Web Scraper API Project

Author: Volkan AYDIN
Year: 2025
Contact: volkan@designmonkeys.net
GitHub: https://github.com/volkandm

This project was developed with passion for web scraping and automation.

Key Contributions:
- Advanced CSS selector syntax with parent navigation
- Unified API design for both single and collection scraping
- Attribute extraction capabilities
- Playwright integration with proxy support
- Professional REST API with authentication
- Comprehensive documentation and examples

Development Timeline:
- January 2025: Initial development and core features
- Advanced selector syntax implementation
- Collection operations with field mapping
- Debug optimization and performance improvements

Technologies Used:
- Python 3.8+
- FastAPI for REST API
- Playwright for browser automation
- Pydantic for data validation
- asyncio for asynchronous operations

Special Thanks:
This project showcases modern web scraping techniques and serves as an educational resource for developers interested in browser automation and API development.

